Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我的複製品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 竟然能夠進行部分變化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個了不起的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒印的控制很熟練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是君麻呂之後最強的複製品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒打算跟你爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要和你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談談
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你從這裡帶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有他在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有他在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就無法離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 你想去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要往前走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有鬼住在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙叫天枰的重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個村子現在已經渺無人煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近他的人沒有能活著回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是嚇唬你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只能跟到這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回自己家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡的人 全都殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒打算跟你爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想把你帶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無法離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉這種傢伙 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分啊 就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是你自己迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是順著你指的方向走下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我欺騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你對我能有什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和佐助兩人獨處了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰想過這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個來找重吾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟重吾一起衝到外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是佐助的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會被輕易幹掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾變強了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是自己投奔大蛇丸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了糾正吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糾正
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以肯定的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於重吾而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸的據點就如同糾正設施一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾想糾正什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說 就像中毒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憑自己無法做到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑制殺人的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無法離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 真是驚人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為會被幹掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂 我來這裡是為了找你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去投奔大蛇丸大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人那裡 你我這樣的人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很孤獨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投奔大蛇丸大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會孤獨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我異於常人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己都無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何時就會殺了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怕你 重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做你的牢籠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的靈魂就是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 從你身體裡提取的酵素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能放入我的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟你一樣 有了咒印的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒印不是誰都能適應的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不適應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣 我就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就別嘗試了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是治療的一個環節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被疾病纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的咒印或許能緩解病毒的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的力量能夠救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是摯友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量沒有拒絕我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下我離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用的能力跟之前不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 水月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是水月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此 這傢伙不好對付哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡不是為了打架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來跟他談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不是光靠動嘴就能擺平的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是用力量把他帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 同歸於盡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…想被我殺掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那股殺意可是真格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷斃了 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把門鎖上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾 我來這裡只是為了把你帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太膽小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再殺人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人格分裂得太嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾自己無法控制殺人的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他無法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他根本不想殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己什麼時候又想去殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我了 快把門鎖上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾果然很危險啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他面前 我都無法安心走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個據點也廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡你就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不錯 我不想再殺人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做你的牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能抑制我的衝動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然君麻呂不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是竹取一族的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸很中意重吾和君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為實驗體 他們一直呆在這個據點裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且君麻呂很強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為珍貴實驗體的重吾暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說只有他才能毫髮無傷地阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個男人 應該已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂已經為我而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你而死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要派你這種病人去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前從沒發生過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我成為大蛇丸大人容器的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的就是把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他值得你這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為容器的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我就只有他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像我的轉生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便拼上性命 也要把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得感謝你啊 重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量讓我更強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所構想的小隊成員就到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 我將我的目的告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的 是殺掉曉的宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波鼬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是他的哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我需要你們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 不是強迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前說過還有別的事 打算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想了下也不著急的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香燐 坦率一點不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你打算一直跟佐助在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰造的謠啊 誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 說中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪你口齒不清呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前你就對佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月 別再招惹香燐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過要彼此合作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直跟著佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到霧隱七刀之一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波鼬的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干柿鬼鮫的大刀鮫肌讓我拿到為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了收集刀啊 真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾 你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂說佐助猶如他的轉生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且拚命保護了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想看看 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是個怎樣的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙為什麼還不回村呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助那傢伙一心想復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了殺掉哥哥宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會去接近曉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後 我們四人就一起行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起 這支小隊的名稱就叫作「蛇」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也盡快開始行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓捕曉的任務還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為了碰到佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最直接的辦法就是去找曉的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我們的目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳特別篇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西外傳 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上 孩子們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西寫輪眼的秘密將會揭開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意圖鎮壓木葉的最強忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑留呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有神秘的三人眾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼上火之意志的戰鬥 現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子由我們來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛞蝓大人 能問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛞蝓大人是怎麼過來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 馬上去小櫻他們那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此 可我走路很慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陽光實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛞蝓大怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽 拿鹽來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼辛苦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家的辛苦比起來 不算什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的不知情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你也來道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是綱手大人用時空間忍術送我過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻的修行還遠遠不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影忍者疾風傳劇場版
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
